name: Nectar for me Pollen for you
description:
This lovely trading is a symbol of love.
as the bee needs nectar for its hive, it will hop from one flower to another, to work, to collect, to do business, and to ensure the pollen and nectar for their children. As the bee moves around it transfers the pollen to the female part of the flower to pollinate them. in this NFT space, we are like bees moving around to collect and give something to sustain the ecosystem of the hive.
